### RAG API 调试文件
### 使用方式：
### 1. 先启动数据库并执行迁移：pnpm migrate:api
### 2. 启动 API：pnpm dev:api
### 3. 先执行 Login，再执行 Create Document，后续请求会复用 accessToken 和 documentId。

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@email = demo@example.com
@password = password123
@deviceName = Local HTTP Client

### Login
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}",
  "deviceName": "{{deviceName}}"
}

### Create Document
# @name createDocument
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/documents
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.data.tokens.accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "RAG Manual Test"
}

### Update Content
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/documents/{{createDocument.response.body.$.data.id}}/content
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.data.tokens.accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": [
    {
      "id": "manual-rag-block-1",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {
        "textColor": "default",
        "backgroundColor": "default",
        "textAlignment": "left"
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "这是一段用于手动验证 RAG 索引的 BlockNote 文本。",
          "styles": {}
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    }
  ]
}

### Get RAG Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/rag/documents/{{createDocument.response.body.$.data.id}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.data.tokens.accessToken}}

### Build RAG Index
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/rag/documents/{{createDocument.response.body.$.data.id}}/index
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.data.tokens.accessToken}}

### Disable Knowledge Base
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/rag/documents/{{createDocument.response.body.$.data.id}}/index
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.data.tokens.accessToken}}
